  <brief_title>Conventional Dose Versus High Dose Sequential Chemotherapy for Poor Prognosis Germ Cell Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase 2 Study of Conventional Dose Chemotherapy Versus High Dose Sequential Chemotherapy as First-line Therapy for Metastatic Poor Prognosis Germ Cell Tumors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
