  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the use of a sequential high dose
      chemotherapy is more effective than conventional dose (i.e. 4 cycles of cisplatin, etoposide,
      and bleomycin [PEB]) in patients with metastatic poor prognosis germ cell tumors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
